'use strict';

const parsers = {
    columnIdent: require('./columnIdent'),
    columnOrPath: require('./columnOrPath'),
    documentField: require('./documentField'),
    documentPath: require('./documentPath'),
    documentPathItem: require('./documentPathItem'),
    documentPathLastItem: require('./documentPathLastItem'),
    documentPathMember: require('./documentPathMember'),
    fieldId: require('./fieldId')
};

const columnOrTableExpressions = options => Object.keys(parsers).reduce((result, current) => {
    return Object.assign({}, result, { [current]: parsers[current].parser(options) });
}, {});

columnOrTableExpressions.Type = Object.keys(parsers).reduce((result, current) => {
    return Object.assign({}, result, { [parsers[current].name]: current });
}, {});

module.exports = columnOrTableExpressions;
